Are you a fan of car traffic games & street racing? Do you like planes and the sky? We have something new to play! Try a plane flying game with different missions, improve your flying skills and become a true professional in racing piloting in Jet Fighter Airplane Racing!

Are you looking for exclusive aeroplanes?
• MiG-21 “Fishbed"
• McDonnell Douglas F-4 Phantom II
• MiG-29 “Fulcrum”
• F-16 Fighting Falcon
• MiG-31 BM “Foxhound”
• F-22 Raptor
• SU-35 “Flanker-E”
• SU-47 "Firkin"
• SU-57
Instructions:
Jet Movement: WASD 
Machine Gun: Space 
Missile: Shift 
Speed Up: ↑
Slow Down: ↓ 
Barrel Roll: Q 
Inside Loop: E 
Heat Traps: R

Multiple modes are waiting for you! Air combat with airplanes, aviation traffic, pursuit of the plane and other armed forces games to discover. Moreover, colorful landscapes are here to make the airplane traffic racer gameplay even better.

Title: Ratatouille: Sara's Cooking Class
Description: Sara’s trying out a new French recipe today. Head to the kitchen and she’ll show you how to prepare it.
Instructions: use your mouse or keyboard to play

Title: Pet Fall
Description: You can move animals from side to side. You have to collect full horizontal lines to make them disappear. Some animals are frozen and must be released twice, some are locked in cages and cannot be moved. Use bonuses when necessary
Instructions: Slide Pet blocks and create full lines. Move Pet blocks to empty positions and create full lines to remove lines.

Title: Blockapolypse Zombie Shooter
Description: Blockapolypse: Zombie Shooter is a defense shooting simulation game with 3D pixel undead creatures. To defend this position, you need to use weapons to defend incoming zombies from 3 directions. After you kill all zombies, you still need to defeat a giant undead creature. As long as you lose all of your HP, you will lose the game. When you earn enough gold coins, you can buy better weapons in the gun shop. Good luck and survive!
Instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

Title: Soccer Dash
Description:
Soccer dash is a soccer game in which you swipe a soccer ball through obstacles and soccer players and hit the ball to score a goal.

You have drag controls, drag to choose the direction of the kick, and release to hit the ball. During the dragging process, the game goes into a slow motion state, so you can take your time to choose the direction of the kick.
Instructions:
The goal of the game is to bypass all the traps and score a goal.
Management - swipe the ball. Change the direction of the kick and release to launch the ball.
Key Features:
? Developing ingenuity and the right trajectory
? Unusual football full of traps
? Slow motion style game
?‍♀️ Fun and creative animation

Title: Magnetic Merge - Number Master
Description:
Merge numbers by adding tiles with the same number to the field next to already placed tiles (vertically or horizontally).
Each merge will create a new tile with a number one higher.

Boosters:
- Remove any tile from the field;
- Remove all tiles with the selected number;
- Refresh: allows to change tile form the "NEXT" up to 5 times.

Each booster is available only once in a single game.

Challenge yourself in this number master merge puzzle. Try to get the higher tile and beet your best score.
Instructions: Left mouse click to interact
Key Features: One touch control

Title: Volley Beans - Volleyball Game
Description: Get ready to become the best volleyball player of all time! Jump right now into this cute and simple, yet challenging volleyball game!
Instructions: Tap to jump, bounce and smash! That's all you need to know!
Key Features: A lot of characters to customise, a lot of enemies to compete, and a lot of stadiums to unlock!

Title: Bomb Head Hot Potato
Description:
In the game "Bomb Head - Hot Potato" your goal is to stay alive and not die from the bomb in your hand. Drop bombs on your opponents to win! 
Immerse yourself in the exciting world of "Bomb Head - Hot Potato" and prove your survival skills and tactical thinking!
Instructions: The goal of Bomb Head - Hot Potato is to stay alive and defeat your opponents by throwing bombs and avoiding their explosions.
Key Features:
- Arena Survival: Your task is to survive in the arena, avoiding bomb explosions and enemy attacks.  
- Blow up your opponents without getting killed: Throw bombs at your opponents to destroy them, while being careful of your own bombs exploding.  
- Passing new levels: Go through a variety of levels, each of which will present new challenges and obstacles.  
- Buying new skins, bombs and heads: Personalize your character by purchasing new skins, bombs and heads for him to look stylish and unique in the arena.

Title: Doomsday Zombie TD
Description: Doomsday Zombie TD is a cool and exciting tower defense game. You aim to defend your castle from brutal enemy attacks and take down the zombie army. Depending on your defense strategy, you can upgrade your buildings, towers, arsenal, and army. Lead your army to defend the castle and kill the zombie hordes. Enjoy!
Instructions: Tap to play

Title: Color Cocktail
Description: Clients are waiting for drinks from you, quickly prepare drinks for clients and collect points. Combine identical balls to get new fruits. Come on, everyone is waiting for you!
Instructions: Drags the cursor at the top of the container and shoot accurately at the balls to combine identical ones. Each time you combine, the ball gets bigger and fills a glass for your guest!

Title: Amazing Airplane Racer
Description: Amazing Airplane Racer revolutionizes the airborne gaming experience by combining high-speed plane racing with strategic special skills. Maneuver through challenging tracks while collecting power-ups like turbo boosts and shields to outsmart opponents. With stunning graphics and intense multiplayer action, the game delivers an adrenaline-packed aerial competition where skill and strategy take center stage. Are you ready to dominate the skies and become the ultimate airborne champion?

Player 1: Move: ARROW KEYS
Player 2: Move: WASD

Title: Tank Battle  War Commander
Description: Command your army in epic battles in this new world war It is a turn based strategy game where you are in command of tanks and other massive weapons to defend your countryYour goal is to conquer all the territories  and force the enemy to retreat up to the final victoryYou are the commander in chief You must defeat the enemy that has invaded your nation and already installed its armed colony

Title: Murder Case Clue 3D
Description: Murder Case Clue 3D is an exciting 3d escape game. You will play the role of detective, there was a murder recently, you need to find some clues and escape from this dangerous house. Be careful, good luck!
Instructions: WASD to move, slide to change view
Key Features:
- Interesting gameplay in the genre!
- Beautiful & colorful graphics!
- Intuitive interface!
- Easy controls!

Title: The Kitchen - Find the Differences
Description: Try to find all the differences in each picture before the time runs out. Be careful though, do not touch the screen randomly to catch all the differences this way. If you click the wrong area several times, the game is over!
Instructions: When you spot a difference between the images touch or click on it
Key Features:
-beautiful pre-rendered graphics
- Higly detailed backgrounds
- Relaxing game
- 5 different levels to play

Title: Grand Clash Arena
Description:
Grand Clash Arena is a unique war game that offers an action-packed experience.

Key Features of the Game:

-Epic Combat Experience: Showcase your mastery against opponents by using every object at your disposal.

-Drop Weapons and Surprises: Alter the flow of the game with surprise drops from the sky. Surprise your opponents with powerful weapons that suddenly appear and gain an advantage.

Grand Clash Arena offers a unique gaming experience that combines the art of war and strategy.
Instructions: Join now, prove yourself in battles! Use WASD keys to move around the arena, spacebar to jump and right mouse button to hit.
Key Features: Character unlock&upgrade, arena battles, various weapon drops, battle vehicles

Title: Mine Shooter
Description: Defend the MineWorld from the invasion of enemies. At your disposal: assault rifles, pistols, sniper rifles, shotguns, submachine guns, grenade launchers, and bazooka. Destroy creepers before they explode. Dodge huge stone golems. Shoot skeletons and beware of hordes of zombies. Show your skills and save your world!
Instructions:
Mouse - look around
WASD - movement
W + Shift - Run
Space - jump

Left Mouse Button - Shoot
Right Mouse Button (Hold) - Aim
Mouse wheel - next/leading weapon
1-7 - weapon hotkeys
R - reload

F - knife attack 1
Q - knife attack 2
G - throw a grenade

T - inspect the weapon
E - remove / remove weapon

Title: Stack Battle.io
Description:
It is a fun and casual puzzle. In the game, the game screen is fresh and simple, and the cute cartoon style is very eye-catching. The biggest highlight is the addition of tower defense battles to the brick-moving gameplay. The game level is very rich, and the gameplay is very simple. 
You can control the movement of the character by pressing and sliding on the screen.
What the player has to do is to control the character to collect the bricks on the map, stack the bricks and send them to your base. When there are enough bricks, your base will be upgraded and the area will be expanded and the number of tower defenses will be increased. 
When the enemy enters the range of your tower defense, you will be attacked. 
On the contrary, when you enter the range of the enemy tower defense, you will also be attacked. whichever side is attacked and dies first will fail the game, otherwise it will succeed.
Players who like brick-moving games come and download it.
Instructions: The operation method of the game is very simple, you can control the movement of the character by pressing and sliding the screen with your finger
Key Features:
1. The operation method of the game is very simple, you can control the movement of the character by pressing and sliding the screen with your finger

2. What the player has to do is to control the character to move the bricks on the map

3. Then send the bricks back to your base


4. At this time, your base will build a defense tower, which can not only protect you but also resist enemy invasion

5. When the enemy enters the range of your defense tower, it will If you are attacked, you will also be attacked when you enter the enemy's defense tower;

6. When all enemies die, you will win.

Title: Kawaii Memory - Card Matching Game
Description: Kawaii Memory is a fun and adorable card matching game where the goal is to find all the pairs of cards. With cute and colorful cards featuring fruits, slimes, and animals. Test your memory and concentration as you match each card with its identical partner. Challenge yourself and improve your cognitive skills as you progress through the different levels of difficulty. Kawaii Memory is perfect for all ages and is a great way to pass the time while enjoying the cute and fun visuals.
